caption.p: Re protects RF/6A cells via regulation of the PI3K/Akt pathway. (A) Akt and p-AKT expression detected by western blot. (B) The changes of related proteins after LY294002 (PI3K inhibitor) incubation. (C) Analysis of Akt and p-Akt expression. (D– H) Statistic analysis of related protein levels. The results are presented as the mean ± SEM percentage of the control from three independent tests. ## P < 0.01 versus the control group; *P < 0.05, **P < 0.01 versus the HG group; $$ P < 0.01 versus the HG+Re group.
